{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-a90d975465b2782a", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# A Survey on Audio Diffusion Models: Text To Speech Synthesis and Enhancement in Generative AI\narXiv: 2303.13336\nAuthors: Chenshuang Zhang, Chaoning Zhang, Sheng Zheng, Mengchun Zhang, Maryam Qamar, Sung-Ho Bae, In So Kweon\nYear: 2023 | Venue: \nTopic: \nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. Provides the first comprehensive survey specifically focused on recent progress in diffusion-based speech synthesis.\n  2. Categorizes text-to-speech diffusion methods into three distinct groups based on the model stage: acoustic model, vocoder, and end-to-end framework.\n  3. Classifies speech enhancement tasks into two types depending on whether specific signals are removed from or added to the input speech.\n  4. Includes comparisons of experimental results and detailed discussions across the reviewed methods.\n\nTags: TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, Vocoder/Diffusion", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "9a26a343-e551-4bcd-a340-1ad6d179b417", "uuid": "b5b25989-2b53-451f-8760-80ebfb148df2", "timestamp": "2026-07-14T16:06:45.092Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# A Survey on Audio Diffusion Models: Text To Speech Synthesis and Enhancement in Generative AI\narXiv: 2303.13336\nAuthors: Chenshuang Zhang, Chaoning Zhang, Sheng Zheng, Mengchun Zhang, Maryam Qamar, Sung-Ho Bae, In So Kweon\nYear: 2023 | Venue: \nTopic: \nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. Provides the first comprehensive survey specifically focused on recent progress in diffusion-based speech synthesis.\n  2. Categorizes text-to-speech diffusion methods into three distinct groups based on the model stage: acoustic model, vocoder, and end-to-end framework.\n  3. Classifies speech enhancement tasks into two types depending on whether specific signals are removed from or added to the input speech.\n  4. Includes comparisons of experimental results and detailed discussions across the reviewed methods.\n\nTags: TTS/架构-NAR-Diffusion, Vocoder/Diffusion", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
